Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:16.68,ED-CN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\fax-0.3\c&HFFFFFF&}都是星光閃耀的最後瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:21.80,ED-JP,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\fax-0.3\c&HFFFFFF&}諦観 それも今となりゃ野暮か
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:21.80,ED-CN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\fax-0.3\c&HFFFFFF&}是看破一切 還是渾渾噩噩
